"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/38/19050?source=see_link\">",
"      Etiology of hearing impairment in children",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?21/40/22153?source=see_link\">",
"      Otitis media with effusion (serous otitis media) in children",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/38/36457?source=see_link\">",
"      Prevention and management of tympanostomy tube otorrhea in children",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <br/>",
